{"tid":1690058,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聖保羅男女中學 打壓靜坐被轟","createTime":"2019-11-03T06:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T07:27:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"99254f9f80ed5c47bab171de63cc51fd45cc9b6a","tid":1690058,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:34:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191103/XJBNJ3HSZBLPR4OWB5OALALFBY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191103%2FXJBNJ3HSZBLPR4OWB5OALALFBY%2F&d=AnzAvEp6rraOVT5%2FQxAiQdEgU5aikFnqk5iyu2dsMw0%3D&h=bff56600\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191103%2FXJBNJ3HSZBLPR4OWB5OALALFBY%2F&h=6ff8be6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191103/XJBNJ3HSZBLPR4OWB5OALALFBY/</a><br />\n<br />\n聖保羅男女中學 打壓靜坐被轟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/tMHOzHb4416CqCgN-LOK5tffEww=/802x502/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/CZG4O72AAWONC57ZXLDYLZDANU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FtMHOzHb4416CqCgN-LOK5tffEww%3D%2F802x502%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FCZG4O72AAWONC57ZXLDYLZDANU.gif&h=085599b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n12間學校發聯署聲明，轟聖保羅男女中學校董會顛倒是非，箝制學生表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n聖保羅男女中學校董會上周向學生家長發信，批評學生在校外戴口罩靜坐屬違法，表示所有人均不可利用學校作平台，在校內宣示政治立場，引起學生及校友強烈反彈。多間中學反修例關注組昨日聯合聲明，表示對聖保羅校董會顛倒是非，箝制學生表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：保時捷播《榮光》警強拖司機落車㩒地押走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12校學生聯署<br />\n<br />\n聯署聲明題為〈千磨萬擊還堅勁 任爾東西南北風──聲援聖保羅男女中學學生聯校聲明〉，內文指，聖保羅男女校董會的家長信以保護為名、打壓為實，列舉多項規條欺壓聖保羅學生，12間學校關注組對聖保羅校董會的惡行甚為不齒。<br />\n<br />\n聲明稱，聖保羅校董會一方提到其教育綱領為培養學生各方才能及兼濟之心，但另一方又阻撓學生參與公民社會活動，動機實在令人費解。<br />\n<br />\n近月事件不單顯露制度崩壞、公權失衡，政府執意與民為敵，香港聖公會及聖保羅校董會成員身為受教育人士，又自詡深明教育的本質及意義，卻處處限制學生表達意見的途徑，並揚言會以紀律處分懲處違規學生，散播白色恐怖，自甘墮落。<br />\n<br />\n參與聯署聲明的關注組來自聖若瑟書院、聖士提反女子中學、喇沙書院等12間學校，他們指出，威嚇只會使學生更加團結，打壓學生只會使他們更堅強，「因為我們是活在在威權政治下被嚇大的一代」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者白琳"},{"pid":"524f16706778e4e942c84fb73b7a9d542236fc67","tid":1690058,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:35:15.000Z","msg":"係微博撐警 表掦香港警察 再踩低公安解放軍 !!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689332</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9f3bfdb376ef64013ff617280d6ff77cf43d8fd7","tid":1690058,"uid":76690,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:35:58.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 榮譽港大副學士"},{"pid":"88af9fc983c8e3db7e9a986110d4befeb336f9d4","tid":1690058,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f3bfdb376ef64013ff617280d6ff77cf43d8fd7","tid":1690058,"uid":76690,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:35:58.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 榮譽港大副學士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:42:47.000Z","msg":"做乜啫你...佢目的係分化對面"},{"pid":"27689a8c9753c90fedeb82571f65ca0fefd7c7b1","tid":1690058,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:44:41.000Z","msg":"發夢中後排可唔可以click入黎睇睇 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出到黎可唔可以緊張少少 審時度勢..<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689923</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d6d77f71a59ea5764d5c81293be879d7592596b8","tid":1690058,"uid":112878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:07:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a887ea3273955115627740a6503786503b66d72b","tid":1690058,"uid":294916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:27:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}